
## Developer Knowledge Compiler (DKC)

This project uses DKC to accumulate developer knowledge. Knowledge base: `.knowledge/`

### Quick Commands
- `/reflect` — Compile knowledge from recent coding session
- `/gaps` — Show knowledge gaps and blind spots
- `/concept <name>` — Look up a concept page
- `/learned` — Summary of what you've learned recently
- `/status` — Knowledge base health overview

